  abstract      = "Cortical circuits exhibit intricate recurrent architectures
                   that are remarkably similar across different brain areas.
                   Such stereotyped structure suggests the existence of common
                   computational principles. However, such principles have
                   remained largely elusive. Inspired by gated-memory networks,
                   namely long short-term memory networks (LSTMs), we introduce
