  author   = "Wyatte, Dean and Jilk, David J and O'Reilly, Randall C",
  abstract = "Standard models of the visual object recognition pathway hold
              that a largely feedforward process from the retina through
              inferotemporal cortex leads to object identification. A
              subsequent feedback process originating in frontoparietal areas
              through reciprocal connections to striate cortex provides
