  abstract      = "In this paper, we present an approach for Recurrent
                   Iterative Gating called RIGNet. The core elements of RIGNet
                   involve recurrent connections that control the flow of
                   information in neural networks in a top-down manner, and
                   different variants on the core structure are considered. The
                   iterative nature of this mechanism allows for gating to
