              ubiquitous recurrent connections in biological brains are
              essential for task performance.",
  journal  = "Front. Psychol.",
  volume   =  8,
  pages    = "1551",
  month    =  sep,
  year     =  2017,
  keywords = "convolutional neural network; object recognition; occlusion;
              recurrent neural network; top-down processing",
  language = "en"
}

@INPROCEEDINGS{Michaelis2018-ia,
