              simpler than other deep ANNs in terms of the number of
              convolutions performed along the longest path of information
              processing in the model. All CORnet models are available at
              https://github.com/dicarlolab/CORnet, and we plan to update this
              manuscript and the available models in this family as they are
              produced.",
  journal  = "bioRxiv",
  pages    = "408385",
  month    =  sep,
  year     =  2018,
  keywords = "k99\_connectomics",
  language = "en"
