              fixed piecewise polynomial, the VC dimension is between wk and
              w2k.•• For architectures with activation $\sigma$=H (threshold
              nets), the VC dimension is between w log(kw) and min\{wklogwk, w2
              + wlogwk\}.•• For the standard sigmoid $\sigma$(x)= 1(1 + e−x),
