               effective for classifying imbalanced data and allows CNNs to
               produce crisp boundaries. Moreover, we propose an end-to-end
               network which adopts the bottom-up/top-down architecture to
               tackle the task. The proposed network effectively leverages
               hierarchical features and produces pixel-accurate boundary mask,
