  author   = "Lin, I-Chun and Okun, Michael and Carandini, Matteo and Harris,
              Kenneth D",
  abstract = "Although cortical circuits are complex and interconnected with
              the rest of the brain, their macroscopic dynamics are often
              approximated by modeling the averaged activities of excitatory
              and inhibitory cortical neurons, without interactions with other
              brain circuits. To verify the validity of such mean-field models,
