                   primate ventral visual stream'', fails to capture essential
                   characteristics of human behavioural data and behaves
                   essentially like a standard purely feedforward ResNet-50 in
                   our analysis. Taken together, error consistency analysis
                   suggests that the strategies used by human and machine
                   vision are still very different -- but we envision our
                   general-purpose error consistency analysis to serve as a
                   fruitful tool for quantifying future progress.",
  month         =  jun,
