              section. Further validation of this algorithm or an improved
              algorithm may have value to more accurately assess percentage of
              malignant cells for companion diagnostic mutation testing.",
  journal  = "Appl. Immunohistochem. Mol. Morphol.",
  volume   =  22,
  number   =  5,
  pages    = "363--371",
  month    =  may,
