              Javaherian, Ashkan and Serre, Thomas and Finkbeiner, Steven",
  abstract = "Cellular events underlying neurodegenerative disease may be
              captured by longitudinal live microscopy of neurons. While the
              advent of robot-assisted microscopy has helped scale such efforts
              to high-throughput regimes with the statistical power to detect
              transient events, time-intensive human annotation is required. We
