                   via another, often inaccurate proxy (e.g., FLOPS), our
                   approach directly measures real-world inference latency by
                   executing the model on mobile phones. To further strike the
                   right balance between flexibility and search space size, we
                   propose a novel factorized hierarchical search space that
                   encourages layer diversity throughout the network.
